29:00.066 --> 29:01.763
No, I studied
in the States, too.

29:01.850 --> 29:03.548
Yeah, Cal State Fullerton.

29:03.635 --> 29:05.550
- I majored in Thought.
- Mmm.

29:05.637 --> 29:07.769
