Psst, P.T.

30:12.269 --> 30:13.792
Hmm?

30:13.879 --> 30:15.315
Look over here.

30:15.402 --> 30:16.751
She's a hottie.

30:16.838 --> 30:19.232
This is the kind of girl
you should date.

30:19.319 --> 30:23.323
Smart, beautiful.
